{"tid":1561393,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"未買、要買 廢老咭嘅入一入","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T23:33:44.000Z","uid":110757,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7e9868061415f3a52c9ccca588d8be0e1dbaba95","tid":1561393,"uid":110757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"尋晚我阿爺報夢比我，講咗以下呢對廢話<br />\n<br />\n「乖孫唔使驚、唔使同佢講咁撚多廢話，直接行埋佢話要一張<span style=\"color: orange;\">迷你廢老咭</span>（7仔OK都有）<br />\n買嗰陣佢淨係會問你需唔需要增值因為入邊冇錢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">至於點解要買迷你版</span></span><br />\n係因為個人覺得易啲收藏拆開個殼攝喺邊度都得，記住唔好退咗自己原本個張，有咩實時比人查票比人逗就一鳩整撚爛張廢老晶片，用自己原本個張比佢地查<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「個閘壞咗sense唔到，關我撚事呀？屌你老母黨鐵」</span></span>」<br />\n你地有冇睇立場黃大仙站個live？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個學生哥偷跳落幾十隻</span>"},{"pid":"b91208b4fc1875f5869e7a33f13f58250bc7e6b0","tid":1561393,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div s